{
  "stem": "21013.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent me [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] postal money orders so I could get a little money out of it and pocket money.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then, of course, I was lucky enough to have them come later on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people in England, my foster homes, were very wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had to move 18 times, because none of them thought I would be there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- I had a transit visa for three months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But my-- to-- to England.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] But my American visa didn't come through, because the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And during the war, there was no way of getting across.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I left in November 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The war had broken out in September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I went on a French ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By that time, the was sinking in New York Harbor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was tilting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the French Line didn't want to give me any passage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They said that the ticket that I had the money was in Vienna and they never got that money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The Refugee Committee then supplied me with a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they fought and said, you got the money out right away, which they did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they gave me a passage on the smallest French Line ship, the instead of the largest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was a blacked-out ship all painted gray with guns mounted on the decks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was a gunrunner, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it took 21 days to come across the Atlantic, while mines were swept loose and U-boats attacked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were under constant U-boat attack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then we got to New York Harbor safely.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
